{"tid":1732443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淺水鯉魚終有難，百載繁華一夢消。 勇武少左一大半，運動開始走向終結","createTime":"2019-11-18T01:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T01:51:04.000Z","uid":30561,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f6aeaa577f35a28239c946e8317b86670cdc333b","tid":1732443,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:42:25.000Z","msg":"香港從此。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n樓壘閣聳雲霄，車水馬龍竟夕囂。 淺水鯉魚終有難， 百載繁華一夢消。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一大批無裝離開POLY既人己被拘補<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/uuddu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fuuddu&d=Iox0GB6uY5Umm6P4cmuVhxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=6299f9d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/uuddu</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66NEP2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66NEP2a.png&h=07749e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/XnWNY8z.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n理大校長滕錦光錄影發言 籲示威者自首</span></span><br />\n<br />\n警方凌晨 5 時許攻入理大校園，拘捕多人後撤退，理大校長滕錦光之後透過公關向傳媒發放片段，指滕錦光曾希望到現場和學生交流，但警方認為危險不適合，所以他錄製片段。<br />\n<br />\n滕錦光在片段中指，自昨日下午一直和警方溝通，獲警方承諾若示威者不主動攻擊，警方會暫緩攻勢，警方亦容許校內人士和平離開校園，膝錦光會陪同前往警署，確保他們的個案獲公平處理，希望示威者接受建議，和平離開校園。"},{"pid":"4f2fe7f9d4b87ab0b4ebb9d516df3d0835e1eecb","tid":1732443,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:42:44.000Z","msg":"淺水鯉魚終有難，百載繁華一夢消。 勇武少左一大半，運動開始走向終結"},{"pid":"481bfaf32f507f308e341ec885d3194f5b802f6c","tid":1732443,"uid":52939,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:44:05.000Z","msg":"ended"},{"pid":"edc9c0e94a2e4abb821bad2efbcc8df8724635fa","tid":1732443,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/mZSxq7u.png\" />"},{"pid":"fe7c5e08f59301c072f74bf